description: Earlier this year I was overseas in Indonesia filming a short documentary for a Non-Profit, called Access Life International. On our way in to the mountains of Bali to meet a village leader, I saw this forest of beautiful bright green trees. I had never seen anything like it before. My jaw dropped as we passed by. I asked my friend (and host), David, if we could stop so I could take a picture even though it wasn’t related to the project. Needless to say, I got the shot and now cherish the memories my team and I created on our brief stop.
